data.description: It doesn't get much better than this beautifully cared for home, on a corner lot in Belmont Park! New lighting, LVP flooring, updated trim, luxury upgraded carpet with 3/4" foam pad, gorgeous stone fireplace and mantle made with 100 year old barn wood. The custom touches throughout make this home special. The formal dining room could easily be utilized as an office, playroom or make it a grand dining space to enjoy for the holidays. Watch the Texas sunset from the back deck, complete with fire pit. Ring video doorbell, window coverings, refrigerator and added garage overhead storage convey! Newer outdoor AC unit, garage door opener and sprinkler system. This stellar property has everything you need to make it home.
